All Classes

Class Description
Colours
An ENUM class of Color objects that are used for drawing the word cloud fonts.
Drawable
An interface for creating classes that draw objects that can be returned as a BufferedImage.
DrawCloud
The DrawString class contains a method to creates a BufferedImage of the word cloud using a list of input words.
Fonts
An ENUM class of web safe font names that are used for drawing the word cloud.
GenerateCloud
This is a class contains a method that runs the word cloud workflow.
Generator
A builder interface that has one method that is used as a builder class to create complex objects in a step by step process.
Interactible
An interface that allows the user to interact with the application.
MapByHash
The HashMapObject implements the Mappable interface and implements its two methods.
MapByHashRunnable
A Runnable class for finding the frequency of the words that extends HashMapObject.
Mappable
Interface for mapping operations.
Menu
This is a UI menu class for the word cloud generator.
Parseable
A interface for filtering, normalising or parsing objects.
ParseText
This class contains methods to normalise the raw input text.
Rankable
An interface for organising and ranking objects by some ordering.
RankWords
This class implements the Rankable interface.
Runner  
Settings
Settings class that creates an object that stores all the parameters for processing a word cloud (input file name, word count, input text source and number of threads to map word frequency).
Source
An abstract class that implements the Sourceable interface and implements a returnText method.
Sourceable
Interface is for loading a Source object and returning a String.
SourceTxt
An class that implements the Sourceable interface and extends the Source class.
SourceURL
An class that implements the Sourceable interface and extends the Source class.
Threadable
An interface for performing mapping operations concurrently using multi-threading.
ThreadedMap
This is the worker class for running a Runnable Mappable object created using the MapByHashRunnable class.
